<p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 232, 219); font-size: 24px;">会议第一项：团总支书记饶子欢致辞。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 34px; background-color: rgb(255, 232, 219); font-size: 24px;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEL5eE44uybMZsSma31Tpw1B1TWzMdLzZPz8hZ2LabF49BopRic8pjDX4eCjyofeibRllY5NzLL5r8sA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="346" height="222" style="width: 346px; height: 222px;"/></span></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 232, 219); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体;">饶老师对上学期各团支部的工作开展情况予以肯定，感谢各团支书的努力和付出。此外，她向各团支部提出反问</span>“<span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体;">为什么在</span>2022<span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体;">年的年度优秀团员班级评选中有些团支书没能获得同学们的认可？</span>”<span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体;">意在引导各班团支书进行自我思考、自我反省。并对为今后的支部建设做出了明确要求：</span></span></section><p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 232, 219); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; font-family: Calibri;">1.</span>各班团支书不仅要在工作上更加的负责，更要深入班级，了解同学们的真实思想状况，在接下来的各项活动中有所创新，由此激发团员青年们的积极性。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 232, 219); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri;">2.</span>各班团支书要在思想上提认识，活动上显创新，行动中有效率，展示青年团干部的生机与活力。</span></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 232, 219); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: Calibri; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">3.<span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体;">广大团员青年干部要积极参加</span>“<span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体;">学雷锋志愿服务月</span>”<span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体;">主题系列活动，学雷锋精神，建雷锋班级，做雷锋传人，提高青年团学干部的服务意识、奉献精神。</span></span></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>